==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unking
<hw>Un*king"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>king</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cause to cease to be a
king.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Shall his condescension, therefore, <qex>unking</qex> him?</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unkingship</ent>⟦br⟧
